{"tid":1561364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"23歲失蹤男秀茂坪墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T01:58:07.000Z","uid":144201,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7d36afcd5701df3fc01d36ec07fe78e67fd83020","tid":1561364,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"23歲男子朱植雄前日（9日）上午離開秀茂坪秀明道的住所後便告失蹤，其家人同日向警方報案。至今早（11日）11時24分，警方接報，一名男子倒臥於秀茂坪邨秀義樓一天井，救護人員到場證實男子已告不治，現場沒有遺書。警方經調查後，確認死者為朱植雄，相信他從上址天台墮下，事件沒有可疑，其死因仍有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288<br />\n年輕人專線<br />\n香港輔導及心理學會：WhatsApp熱線6218 1084 (提供英語及粵語專業輔導服務)<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線：青少年生命專線 2382 0777<br />\n 大家點睇?"},{"pid":"95385d7d9e9330ca441d200e850563c58da7f674","tid":1561364,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qftu6C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqftu6C0.jpg&h=23ce3992&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cvOSjYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt